    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人救出了名为“幽影”的龙。\\n而后他们得知菲丽嘉和幽影\\n是从死神“塔纳托斯”那里逃脱出来。\\n一行人刚提出要协助他们逃跑，\\n塔纳托斯的手下就突然来袭。众人遂迎击。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "呜……啊啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这是怎么回事！\\n魔兽都聚在一起！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "幽影！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们这就来救你！\\n呀啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "呃……哈啊……哈啊……\\n菲丽嘉……是你吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "嗯，我是菲丽嘉。\\n我带人来救你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "好重的伤……请赶快让我看看！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "各位，谢谢你们了。\\n多亏了你们，他才能得救。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "菲丽嘉，这些人究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "为了救你，\\n他们和我一起来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "是这样啊……\\n烦劳各位了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不过，这样就安心了！\\n大家已经打倒了魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "如果是这样……就好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你那表情，好像另有隐情啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不介意的话，跟我们说说情况吧。\\n那个，你是叫……菲丽嘉吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "是的！我都还没自我介绍……\\n对、对不起！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "我叫菲丽嘉。\\n之前一直被囚禁在魔兽的栖息处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "而解救我的正是幽影。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n所以魔兽才追着你们吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "可是可是，刚才不是\\n已经打倒魔兽了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "它们不过是追捕菲丽嘉的\\n魔兽手下罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "囚禁我的魔兽叫塔纳托斯——\\n它自称为“死神”塔纳托斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "它是拥有收割他人性命之力的魔兽。\\n令人恐惧……身形巨大……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你被那种骇人的家伙囚禁，\\n竟然还能平安无事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "应该是故意让我活下来的吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "塔纳托斯似乎想让我\\n成为只属于他的舞姬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "舞姬？\\n菲丽嘉是靠跳舞谋生的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "是的。我的故乡有一种风俗，\\n为祈祷丰收，会为大地献上舞蹈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "而我就负责跳舞。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶！好厉害！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "但正因如此\\n才会被那家伙盯上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而他为了把献给大地的舞蹈据为己有，\\n才抓走了菲丽嘉吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "是的……正当我在村子的祭典上\\n表演舞蹈时，塔纳托斯突然出现……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "求你了！\\n请放我回村子吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塔纳托斯",
            "context": "你的归所\\n已经不是那个村子了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塔纳托斯",
            "context": "今后你要在这个昏暗的世界里\\n只为我而起舞。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塔纳托斯",
            "context": "好了，跳吧，我的舞姬！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "我被囚禁在塔纳托斯的栖息处之后，\\n无数次想要逃跑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "可是……每次我逃跑都会被抓回去，\\n正当我以为已经无法逃脱的时候……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "幽影挺身而出对抗塔纳托斯，\\n带着我逃了出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "所以你成功脱逃之后，\\n塔纳托斯就派追兵来追你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不过，能找到被魔兽囚禁的女孩，\\n你也真厉害啊，幽影。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "因为她楚楚动人的身影\\n吸引了我的目光。\\n那是带着一丝忧伤的舞姿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "被她吸引，\\n是说对她一见钟情了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "为什么会说到这个……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "如果不是这个理由，\\n我就难以理解了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "“你”可没有不惜冒着危险\\n也要救这个女孩的道义嘛。\\n毕竟你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "闭嘴，绯龙。\\n过去的事就不要再提了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "救菲丽嘉没什么特别的理由，\\n只是出于同情而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "唔……因为同情而出手相救，\\n那接下来要怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "我会送菲丽嘉\\n回到她的家乡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "是我擅自带她出来的，\\n所以我会负责让她回归原本的生活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "哪有……说什么擅自！\\n我感谢你都来不及呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "不过，幽影……\\n我回去没问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "咦？\\n你不想回去吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "塔纳托斯一定不会放过我。\\n我就算回去了，\\n村子也会陷入危机。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "虽说我想回去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我懂了。\\n菲丽嘉，我们去你的村子吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们会保护你和村子的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "咦！？可、可是塔纳托斯\\n可能会追过来哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "如果它追过来，\\n我们就打倒他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊。那种肆意摧毁人们\\n安稳生活的魔兽可不能放任不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "就算你侥幸逃过一劫，\\n也没准会出现下一个受害者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "很让人安心不是吗，菲丽嘉？\\n这下你就不用担心了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "各位……谢谢你们。\\n虽然很过意不去，但还是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "请带我回村子吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，没问题。\\n那我们就出发……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不会让你逃走……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塔纳托斯",
            "context": "不会让你逃走……不会让你逃走！\\n菲丽嘉，我心爱的舞姬啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "塔纳托斯",
            "context": "我绝不会让你逃走……\\n不会把你交给任何人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "被包围了！？而且这声音\\n好像在哪里听到过！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "幽影",
            "context": "现在先集中精力对付眼前的敌人！\\n是塔纳托斯的手下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "菲丽嘉",
            "context": "啊，啊啊……我果然还是\\n无法逃出塔纳托斯的掌心吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "会有办法的！\\n我刚才也说了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们会保护你！\\n各位，一起打倒魔兽吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20406_02_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}